OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780617775
OL,3,CAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor earned
OL,4,Cincome from Royal Lodge cottage sublets
OL,6,FThe Talking Royals team discuss how
OL,7,Fmuch of the Royal Family's living
OL,8,Fexpenses are paid for
OL,10,FThe former prince was allowed to keep
OL,11,Fthe rental income from the tenants
OL,12,Fhimself, and the arrangements only
OL,13,Fceased in April of this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
