OL,3,CAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor earned
OL,4,Cincome from Royal Lodge cottage sublets
OL,6,FAndrew is technically entitled to
OL,7,F#301,000 in compensation for moving
OL,8,Fout early, although it has been
OL,9,Fsuggested by the Crown Estate that he
OL,10,Fdidn't keep up the repairs as he had
OL,11,Fpromised, and the dilapidated state of
OL,12,FRoyal Lodge means compensation would
OL,13,Fbe unlikely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
