CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780617775
OL,3,CAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor earned
OL,4,Cincome from Royal Lodge cottage sublets
OL,6,FPalace insiders did suggest the
OL,7,Fcurrent arrangements would be kept
OL,8,Funder review, which suggests the
OL,9,Farrangements for Beatrice and Eugenie
OL,10,Fand their husbands may not continue
OL,11,Ffor too much longer.
OL,13,FNormally, the rent for properties in
OL,14,FOccupied Royal Palaces for those who
OL,15,Fare not working royals is worked out
OL,16,Fat 60% of the market value, given that
OL,17,Fthe homes are inside a security cordon
OL,18,Fand therefore unable to be let on the
OL,19,Fopen market.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
