OL,3,CAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor earned
OL,4,Cincome from Royal Lodge cottage sublets
OL,6,FRent-free arrangements are in place
OL,7,Ffor those who work full-time for the
OL,8,FMonarchy, which includes the Prince
OL,9,Fand Princess of Wales (at Kensington
OL,10,FPalace), Princess Anne, and the Duke
OL,11,Fand Duchess of Gloucester, who are
OL,12,Fcousins of the late Queen.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
