OL,3,CAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor earned
OL,4,Cincome from Royal Lodge cottage sublets
OL,6,FPrince William and Kate have their own
OL,7,Farrangement with the Crown Estate for
OL,8,Fthe family home they recently occupied
OL,9,Fin Windsor, but their landlords paid
OL,10,Fout nearly #400,000 for repairs before
OL,11,Fthey moved in.
OL,13,FForest Lodge, on the Windsor Estate,
OL,14,Fis where the couple live with their
OL,15,Fthree children, Prince George,
OL,16,FPrincess Charlotte and Prince Louis.
OL,18,FThey agreed a 'short-term lease' of 20
OL,19,Fyears with the Crown Estate and pay
OL,20,Fjust over #300,000 each year in
OL,21,Fquarterly instalments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
