CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780617775
OL,3,CAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor earned
OL,4,Cincome from Royal Lodge cottage sublets
OL,6,FWilliam and Catherine's office says
OL,7,Fthe couple funded the internal
OL,8,Fredecorations themselves after the
OL,9,Flandlord had paid for the major repair
OL,10,Fworks.
OL,12,FSenior royal sources suggested the
OL,13,Fmoney Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor
OL,14,Fcharged in rent for the cottages at
OL,15,FRoyal Lodge was calculated to cover
OL,16,Fmaintenance and running costs rather
OL,17,Fthan to make a profit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
